{"tid":952343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係金拱門最後一日有飲筒","createTime":"2018-12-23T05:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T06:27:12.000Z","uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2a25d5abf9f2451efb0bca782b9d821e34e7cf47","tid":952343,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T05:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181220/large/1545283281_fb68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181220%2Flarge%2F1545283281_fb68.jpg&h=06fd2ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以後唔再食老麥<br />\n<br />\n麥當勞再宣佈，由12月24日起全線麥當勞及McCaf&eacute;將每日推行「麥麥走飲管」，藉此鼓勵減少使用膠飲管<br />\n除特定飲品如凍港式奶茶、咖啡、鮮檸檬茶、奶昔、冰雪等會提供管形匙羹外，全港麥當勞及McCaf&eacute;會收起飲管箱內的所有飲管，亦不會主動隨飲品派發飲管，而需要攪拌的飲品會使用木攪拌棒取代以往的塑膠攪拌棒。"},{"pid":"4da3132fa84f4d8f57a279bea679f7707af05e51","tid":952343,"uid":66680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T05:18:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老母環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c4efad9f74c56efc9ab2e6fb0889aee46ee55b","tid":952343,"uid":172606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"無得用飲筒，我驚唔小心倒瀉倒到周圍都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce9083218f0085c4fe7cace4bd5a634758494cd","tid":952343,"uid":191765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"唔用飲管會容易導致蛀牙 從而影響人的健康狀況 令到醫療開支大增 政府經濟增加 令香港經濟體系受損 影響國際地位 從而進一步以蝴蝶效應影響整個世界嘅經濟體系 更有機會引發不同國家的貿易戰 甚至